			<item>
				<title>Devlog 1 - What is A Beacon?</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/posts/devlog-001/</link>
				<pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 16:48:48 +0100</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/devlog-001/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;A Beacon is a point-and-click adventure set in a dark medieval fantasy world, with humor — actual humor, not the odd giggle buried in 14 hours of fetch quests. I am heavily influenced by Monkey Island, Monty Python and early Blackadder comedy-stylings.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Build wise it is a solo project I&amp;rsquo;m working on using s&amp;amp;box engine and illustrating everything by hand in Adobe Fresco. It&amp;rsquo;s early days but yeah.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here is a snippet of game play and some screen shots so far. I don&amp;rsquo;t want to give away too much so here&amp;rsquo;s a sneak-peak. More too come as and when 🪦&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
